msgid "producing a trailer of the form::"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:208 09ee486a2bef4d4a8cd93e63103f7ef5
msgid ""
"Use your real legal name and an email you control. A pull request whose "
"commits lack a valid ``Signed-off-by`` trailer will not be merged."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:212 e1fc3bc2d2684fe88009774ee0297bc9
msgid "If you forget the sign-off on a commit you have already pushed:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/community/contributing.rst:224 832513784cce4b698feb00916c0df5f7
msgid ""
"A maintainer cannot sign on your behalf — sign-off is the contributor's "
"own certification."
msgstr ""

